    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into chunks</p><p>Peel and cut your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> into quarters, then separate the wedges so you end up with a pile of onion petals</p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1707144494456-x200.jpg",
