        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the veg is roasting, wipe clean the reserved bowl and add your <strong>mayo</strong> with your <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong>, a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Add a splash of <strong>cold water</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> garlic mayo</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
