        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the roast veg is ready, remove the tray[s] from the oven and make 1 well per person in the roast veg</p><p>Add the <strong>spinach </strong>and return the tray[s] to the oven for 2 min or until slightly wilted</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
