            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once slightly wilted, remove the tray[s] from the oven and crumble your <strong>Greek cheese </strong>around the spinach</p><p>Crack your <strong>egg[s]</strong> onto the spinach with a grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 5-6 min or until the egg is done to your liking – this is your <strong>Greek cheese & egg tray bake</strong></p><p>Combine<strong> half </strong>your <strong>crispy onions </strong>with the<strong> garlic mayo </strong>– this is your <strong>crispy onion garlic mayo</strong></p>",
