      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Greek cheese &</strong> <strong>egg tray bake</strong> and garnish with the <strong>remaining crispy onions</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> crispy onion garlic mayo </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
